@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Khôi phục mật khẩu
autonumber

actor "Người dùng" as User
boundary "reset_password.html" as ResetPage
control "ForgotPasswordController" as Ctrl
participant "PasswordResetService" as Service
participant "UserRepository" as UserRepo
participant "PasswordResetRepository" as ResetRepo
database "Database" as DB

User -> ResetPage: Click Link reset password
ResetPage -> Ctrl: GET /reset-password(token)
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> Service: validateToken(token)
activate Service

Service -> ResetRepo: findByToken(token)
activate ResetRepo
ResetRepo -> DB: SELECT * FROM password_resets WHERE token = ?
activate DB
DB --> ResetRepo: PasswordReset Object
deactivate DB
ResetRepo --> Service: PasswordReset Object
deactivate ResetRepo

alt Token hợp lệ
    Service --> Ctrl: PasswordReset Object
    Ctrl --> ResetPage: Hiển thị form nhập mật khẩu mới
else Token lỗi/hết hạn
    Service --> Ctrl: null
    Ctrl --> ResetPage: Thông báo lỗi
end

deactivate Service
deactivate Ctrl

User -> ResetPage: Nhập mật khẩu mới
ResetPage -> Ctrl: POST /reset-password(token,password)
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> Service: updatePassword(reset,password)
activate Service

Service -> UserRepo: save(User)
Service -> ResetRepo: save(isUsed=true)

Service --> Ctrl: Success
Ctrl --> ResetPage: Đổi mật khẩu thành công

deactivate Service
deactivate Ctrl

@enduml